scene_description_enriched: The image depicts Saint Sebastian, a young man with fair hair, bound to a tree trunk. He is pierced by numerous arrows, with blood dripping from the wounds. He wears a white loincloth. The background shows a landscape with trees and a body of water under a blue sky. To the left, a rudimentary structure resembling a haystack or a small building is visible. The scene is framed by an arched border with decorative elements.
